# Coffee Shop Sales Dashboard

## Project Overview

This project is an end-to-end Excel data analytics dashboard built using the **Coffee Shop Sales** dataset from Maven Analytics. The dataset contains transaction records for Maven Roasters, a fictitious coffee shop operating across three NYC locations, including transaction date, time, store location, and product-level details.

Dataset source: Maven Analytics Data Playground  
License: Public Domain

## Objective

The objective of this project is to analyze coffee shop sales performance and identify business insights related to:

Total sales
Total footfall
Average bill per person
Average order per person
Sales by product category
Store location performance
Hourly ordering patterns
Weekday order trends
Product and size distribution

## Tools Used

Microsoft Excel
Pivot Tables
